\c 5
\p
\v 1 Zvino kana mweya ukatadza, ndokunzwa inzwi remhiko\x + 1 Madz. 8.31. Mat. 26.63.\x*, uye uve chapupu, kana wakazviona kana kuziva, kana asingatauri, zvino achatakura kuipa kwake\x + 5. 17; 7.18; 10.17; 17.16; 19.8; 20.17,19. Num. 5.31; 20.20; 9.13.\x*.
\v 2 Uye kana mweya ukabata chero chinhu chisina kuchena\x + 11.24,28,31,39. Num. 19.11,13,16.\x*, kana chitunha chemhuka isina kuchena, kana chitunha chechipfuwo chisina kuchena, kana chitunha chezvinokambaira zvisina kuchena, kunyange zvikava zvakavanzika kwaari, achava asina kuchena, agova nemhosva\x + 5.17.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino kana akabata kusachena kwemunhu\x + 12.1,2; 13.1,2; 15.1,2.\x*, kungava kusachena kwake kupi kwaasina kuchena nako, uye kukavanzika kwaari, iye paachaziva achava nemhosva.
\v 4 Zvino kana mweya uchipika, uchitaura usingafungisisi nemiromo \add yawo\add*\x + Map. 106.33; Num. 30.6,8; Zvir. 12.18.\x* kuita chakaipa kana kuita chakanaka\x + 1 Sam. 25.22. Mako 6.23. Mab. 23.12.\x*, kana chii munhu chaangataura asingafungisisi nemhiko, uye chikavanzika kwaari, iye paachaziva, achava nemhosva kune chimwe chaizvozvo.
\v 5 Zvino kuchati kana akava nemhosva pane chimwe chaizvozvo, achabvuma kuti wakatadza pane izvozvo\x + 16.21; 26.40; Num. 5.7; Ezi. 10.1; Josh. 7.19.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino achauya nechipo chake chekudarika kuna Jehovha pamusoro pechivi chake chaakatadza, hadzi kubva pazvipfuwo, gwayana kana mbudzana yembudzi, chive chipo chezvivi; mupristi agomuitira chiyananiso pamusoro pechivi chake.
\v 7 Zvino kana ruoko rwake rusingananaviri kune zvinodiwa pagwayana, ipapo achavigira Jehovha njiva mbiri\x + 1.14.\x*, kana vana vaviri vehangaiwa \add pa\add*kudarika kwake kwaakatadza; imwe yechipo chezvivi, uye imwe yechipo chinopiswa.
\v 8 Zvino achauya nazvo kumupristi, iye achapa iri yechipo chezvivi kutanga, ndokumonyorora musoro wayo pamutsipa wayo, asi arege kuiparadzanisa\x + 1.15,17.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino achasasa \add rimwe\add* reropa rechipo chezvivi parutivi rwearitari, uye rinosara paropa richasvinirwa\x + 1.15.\x* pazasi pearitari\x + 4.7,18,30,34.\x*; chipo chezvivi.
\v 10 Yechipiri ngaaite chipo chinopiswa, zvichienderana nechimiso; uye mupristi achamuitira chiyananiso pamusoro pechivi chake chaakatadza\x + 4.20,26,31,35; 4.13,16.\x*, zvino achachikanganwirwa.
\p
\v 11 Asi kana ruoko rwake rwusingananaviri kunjiva mbiri kana vana vaviri vehangaiwa, zvino uyo anotadza achauya nechipo chake chegumi cheefa cheupfu hwakatsetseka, chive chipo chezvivi; asaisa mafuta pamusoro pahwo, kana kuisa zvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira pamusoro pahwo, nokuti chipo chezvivi\x + Num. 5.15.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino achauya nacho kumupristi, mupristi agotora ruoko rwake ruzere rwahwo\x + 2.2.\x*, \add chive\add* chirangaridzo chahwo, ndokupisa paaritari, zvichienderana nezvipo zvemoto zvaJehovha; chipo chezvivi\x + 4.35; 1.9.\x*.
\v 13 Zvino mupristi achamuitira chiyananiso\x + 4.20,26,31,35; 5.10,16.\x* maererano nechivi chaakatadza pachipi chezvinhu izvi, zvino achachikanganwirwa. Zvino zvichava zvemupristi\x + 2.3.\x*, sechipo chechidyiwa.
\p
\v 14 Zvino Jehovha wakataura kuna Mozisi achiti:
\v 15 Kana mweya ukadarika nekudarika, ukatadza usingazivi pazvinhu zvitsvene zvaJehovha\x + 22.14. Ezi. 10.2.\x*, uchauya nechipo chawo chemhosva kuna Jehovha, gondohwe risina charingapomerwa paboka\x + Ezi. 10.19.\x*, nemaonero ako \add pa\add*mashekeri esirivha maererano neshekeri repanzvimbo tsvene, chive chipo chemhosva\x + Eki. 38.24.\x*.
\v 16 Zvino achatsiva zvaakatadza pachinhu chitsvene, agowedzera cheshanu chacho pachiri, ndokuchipa kumupristi\x + 6.5; 22.14; 27.13,15,27,31.\x*; mupristi agomuitira chiyananiso negondohwe rechipo chemhosva, zvino achachikanganwirwa\x + 4.26.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Zvino kana mweya ukatadza, nekudarika umwe wemirairo yose yaJehovha\x + 4.2.\x* zvisingafaniri kuitwa, kunyange asingazivi\x + 5.15; 4.2,13,22,27.\x*, zvakadaro une mhosva\x + Ruk. 12.48.\x*, uye uchatakura kuipa kwawo.
\v 18 Zvino uchauya kumupristi negondohwe risina charingapomerwa kubva kuboka\x + 5.15.\x*, nemaonero ako, chive chipo chemhosva; mupristi agomuitira chiyananiso pamusoro pekusaziva kwaakatadza nako asingazivi, zvino achakukanganwirwa\x + 4.26.\x*.
\v 19 Chipo chemhosva; zvirokwazvo une mhosva kuna Jehovha.